<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
<title>Snagify · Dubai's Property Inspection App · RERA &amp; RDC Compliant</title>
<meta name="description" content="Dubai's fastest property inspection app. RDC-valid PDF reports, AI photo analysis, dual digital signatures. Used by 40+ Dubai agencies. Try free.">
<meta name="keywords" content="dubai property inspection, rdc valid report, ejari inspection, check-in inspection dubai, check-out inspection, rental dispute dubai, snagging app dubai, property inspection software, dubai real estate tools, rera inspection">
