            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>An undocumented move-in is the single biggest cause of lost deposits in Dubai. We want every landlord and tenant to have that baseline protection, whether you pay us later or not. You only spend credits when you do a check-out, to prove what the property looked like originally.</p></div></div>
